ay)</div></div></div></div></div><div data-index="458" class="slick-slide" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" style="outline:none;width:0.19305019305019305%"><div><div class="post-custom-container carousel-shadow" title="Xem thêm" role="presentation" tabindex="-1" style="width:100%;display:inline-block"><div class="banner-wrapper"><div class="promotion-tag-wrapper"></div><picture><source media="(min-width: 1024px)" srcSet="https://shinhanfinance.com.vn/-/336x/nginx-cms/assets/news/Banner_2021-05-12-074116.jpg 1x, https://shinhanfinance.com.vn/-/672x/nginx-cms/assets/news/Banner_2021-05-12-074116.jpg 2x"/><source media="(max-width: 1023px)" srcSet="https://shinhanfinance.com.vn/-/168x/nginx-cms/assets/news/Banner_2021-05-12-074116.jpg 1x, https://shinhanfinance.com.vn/-/336x/nginx-cms/assets/news/Banner_2021-05-12-074116.jpg 2x"/><img src="https://shinhanfinance.com.vn/-/336x/nginx-cms/assets/news/Banner_2021-05-12-074116.jpg" alt="banner post" class="banner-post"/></picture></div><div class="caption"><div class="created-date">12/5/2021</div><div class="title">Shinhan Finance thông báo về việc tạm thời dừng hoạt động văn phòng Chi nhánh tại tỉnh Bắc Ninh để thực hiện công tác phòng, chống dịch Covid-19</div></div></div></div></div><div data-index="459" class="slick-slide" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" style="outline:none;width:0.19305019305019305%"><div><div class="post-custom-container carousel-shadow" title="Xem thêm" role="presentation" tabindex="-1" style="width:100%;display:inline-block"><div class="banner-wrapper"><div class="promotion-tag-wrapper"></div><picture><source media="(min-width: 1024px)" srcSet="https://shinhanfinance.com.vn/-/336x/nginx-cms/assets/news/Banner-adjusted.jpg 1x, https://shinhanfinance.com.vn/-/672x/nginx-cms/assets/news/Banner-adjusted.jpg 2x"/><source media="(max-width: 1023px)" srcSet="https://shinhanfinance.com.vn/-/168x/nginx-cms/assets/news/Banner-adjusted.jpg 1x, https://shinhanfinance.com.vn/-/336x/nginx-cms/assets/news/Banner-